c: 19
v: 75
t: "Iti (iwe Muhammad (SAW)): “Uyo akarasika, (Allah) vane ngoni zhinji vachamusvitsira (tambo – gwara rakatwasuka) kwaari kusvikira vaona izvo zvavakavimbiswa, murango kana nguva (yezuva rekumutswa), naizvozvo vachazoziva havo kuti ndiani akaipa pachinzvimbo, uye ndiani akarebwedeka (asina kusimba) kupinda mumwe panyaya dzemauto.” (Iyi ndiyo mhinduro kumubvunzo uri muQur’aan)"